title: Joe Fortenbaugh on best bets for NFL season, Raiders/49ers (Football 07/16)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Joe Fortenbaugh of 95.7 the Game to break down some of his best bets for the upcoming season, talk about a few teams over and unders for the year and break down the Raiders and 49ers from a Vegas perspective.
